### Create Game
POST http://localhost:3000/games
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{GAMEMASTER_TOKEN}}

{
  "name": "Smoke Test",
  "maxPlayers": 25,
  "allowLateJoin": true,
  "autoDrawInterval": 8,
  "winnerLimit": 1
}

### Open Game
POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/open
Authorization: Bearer {{GAMEMASTER_TOKEN}}

### Join Game
POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{pin}}/join
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "SmokePlayer"
}

### Resume Session
POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/players/{{playerId}}/resume
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "resumeToken": "{{resumeToken}}"
}

### Manual Draw
POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/draw
Authorization: Bearer {{GAMEMASTER_TOKEN}}

### Submit Claim
POST http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/players/{{playerId}}/claim
Authorization: Bearer {{PLAYER_TOKEN}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pattern": "ROW_1"
}

### Snapshot
GET http://localhost:3000/games/{{gameId}}/snapshot
Authorization: Bearer {{PLAYER_TOKEN}}
